PluginData.Author: dogboy
PluginData.Tooltip: Customizable ships sounds, makes your ship alive!
PluginData.Description: Adds authentic engine sounds that dynamically respond to your ships speed, maneuvering, startup, hull ambiences and more, providing an immersive GaMInG experience. Choose from a diverse selection of engine addons and switch between them on the move. To add more engines, simply enable them as a client mod. Access menu by presing F1. *Works on the servers aswell.
